<h3>Best Times to Post</h3>
<p>Optimal posting times vary by platform and audience. As a starting point:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> Tuesday through Thursday, 8 AM to 10 AM</li>
<li><strong>X:</strong> Weekdays, 9 AM to 12 PM</li>
<li><strong>Instagram:</strong> Monday through Friday, 11 AM to 1 PM</li>
